                        </div>
                        <p>Our model allows each participant access to four expert mentors throughout the year. We serve through four initiatives (Wellness, Education, Employment, and Financial Literacy), each running for eight weeks, guided by a curriculum that ensures our services are relevant and life changing for our participants. For the larger DeKalb community, we also offer seminars and workshops that are facilitated by professionals in their field of expertise.</p>
